"1. Use the left-hand menu to get around.
2. Add a Renren Android widget, to check news feed, post status, upload photos and check-in right on your desktop.
3. View news feed and homepage by categories through the spinner at the top bar.
4. Go back to top instantly by clicking on the blank of the top bar.
5. Pull down the news feed page or the comment page to refresh.
6. Navigate to Options to modify settings like message notification, cache and brightness etc.
